        "text": "Hello! I'm Rico - I just discovered the podcast a month or two ago - recently enough that I've only ever known it as \"Feeling of Computing\" (which I think is a great name btw). I found it because of Ivan's interview with Miller Puckette which I greatly appreciated as an enjoyer of puredata and computer music person in general. I've been working my way through the back catalog and really love the show's vibes, as the kids say. However, the main reason I am here is to recommend a guitar tuner for iOS: Helix Tuner (<https:\/\/apps.apple.com\/us\/app\/helix-tuner\/id1444576708>). Probably the most I've ever paid for an app but darn it, it was worth it. Ok - nice to meet y'all!",
